## Create Institution

To create an institution, use the POST end point ```/institutions``` with the JSON the following info.

```shell
curl -X POST \
  http://localhost:8081/institutions \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
      "activityYear": 2018,
      "lei": "BANK1LEIFORTEST12345",
      "agency": 9,
      "institutionType": -1,
      "institutionId2017": "",
      "taxId": "02-1234567",
      "rssd": -1,
      "emailDomains":
        ["bank1.com"],
      "respondent":
        {"name": "Bank 1", "state": "", "city": ""},
      "parent":
        {"idRssd": -1, "name": ""},
      "assets": -1,
      "otherLenderCode": -1,
      "topHolder":
        {"idRssd": -1, "name": ""},
      "hmdaFiler": true
    }'
```

key | data type | values
--- | --- | ---
activityYear | int | (4 digit year)
lei | String |
agency | int |
institutionType | int |  
